{"title":"南海女民兵","authors":["张志民"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":4,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"南海女民兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张志民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渡海作战演习"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"螺号声声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海空里绕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姐妹们渡海"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夺“敌”堡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧一紧发髻儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"煞煞腰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"登船好似跨战马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗呼啦出发了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪尖儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——波光里闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舢板儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——浪尖上翘！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"观战的人们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海边上瞧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一阵子夸奖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一阵子笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夸她们的威武，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五尺钢枪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——浑身胆！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱她们的灵巧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨海轻如"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——走天桥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笑声儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还在响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夸声儿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还没落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没想到啊没想到！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眨眼的工夫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——变了调！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“哎呀呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不得了！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂风暴雨举天来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霹雳炸响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大海啸！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪在风中卷！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"船在浪上抛！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卷过来——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪大越显那舢板儿小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劈过去——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小船儿变作了斩浪刀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一场鏖战惊天地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁胜谁负？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——难分晓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海边上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们急得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——直跺脚！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心儿啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"噗噗直往"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——喉咙里跳！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的嚷："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“莫说是群女仔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雁过也要拔层毛！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有的怨："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“这么大的风啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电台为啥没预报？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说电台没预报？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大风球，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早在旗杆上吊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小艇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没出海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抛了锚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪知道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——人家呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"削铁才知钢刀硬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"考的正是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——这一着。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一着啊怎么考？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远处望啊抬眼瞧——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是什么星星啊那么亮？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"道道红光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——掠云霄！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“嘿嘿！过去了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过去了……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南山岛上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——发讯号！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风收雨散，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海天高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姐妹们摇船回来了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海燕，掠空飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗，船头飘！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"观战的人们问惊险？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没想到啊没想到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——人家呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“风浪”二字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都没提。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全部的回答——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是轻轻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声笑……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"练　刺　杀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晓月弯弯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桅尖儿上挂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万缕晨光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——抹簪花！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“一、二——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三、四……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喊声脆！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚步儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——唰唰唰！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿公翘脚儿望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"娃仔墙头扒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞧什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渔家女儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——练刺杀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞧吧，挨个数，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——全来啦！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春珊、彩螺、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大海嫂、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"菱妈妈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿英、阿翠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姐儿俩……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞧吧，一排排，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢枪——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手中握！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刺刀——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亮瓦瓦！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫说赴汤蹈火！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虎口里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——敢拔牙！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“刺——”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀刀横穿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千顷浪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“杀——”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声怒吼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊天涯！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刺！带着血泪仇！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忘不了——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十字街头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗渔霸！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杀！怀着阶级恨！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不准那——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鱼鳖虾蟹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往上爬！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞧吧！瞧她们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——精神抖擞！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲上去！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千山万仞——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚下踏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站下来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万把钢剑——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立地插！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞧吧，瞧她们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——钢铁阵容。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象道城墙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象座坝！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象是当年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——“娘子军”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个是“琼花”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海风吹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂浪打，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渔家女儿练刺杀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十八般武艺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顺手儿拿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为社会主义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——保天下！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪个胆敢来捣乱？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当心！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那抓橹的双手啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——云能拨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浪能驾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妖魔鬼怪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全不怕！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抓几个蟊贼海盗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咳！那算啥！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浅滩里捉蟹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——且当作耍……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}